to take care of yourself?

313
00:16:31,960 --> 00:16:32,679
No...

314
00:16:32,960 --> 00:16:33,760
Listen up.

315
00:16:33,760 --> 00:16:34,679
You're listening to me this time.

316
00:16:34,679 --> 00:16:36,239
You have to go to the hospital!

317
00:16:36,960 --> 00:16:40,080
Okay. I'll do as you say.

318
00:16:40,400 --> 00:16:42,359
You made me worry on purpose,
didn't you?

319
00:17:21,599 --> 00:17:22,640
It's so cold.

320
00:17:26,060 --> 00:17:28,460
(The Colorist)

321
00:17:31,980 --> 00:17:39,700
(Secret)

322
00:17:54,359 --> 00:17:55,119
Kele?

323
00:17:56,479 --> 00:17:57,160
Kele?

324
00:17:58,319 --> 00:17:59,880
Take a break if you're tired.

325
00:17:59,880 --> 00:18:01,119
I'll look for the evidence.

326
00:18:02,000 --> 00:18:03,680
No, I'm fine.

327
00:18:04,000 --> 00:18:05,560
It's just...
We've been looking for it for so long.

328
00:18:06,079 --> 00:18:07,280
But we still don't know where it is.

329
00:18:08,079 --> 00:18:09,800
This book here says that

330
00:18:10,079 --> 00:18:12,319
