all day long here.

335
00:18:20,800 --> 00:18:22,479
Where is the evidence?

336
00:18:23,680 --> 00:18:24,839
What about your book?

337
00:18:26,439 --> 00:18:28,280
Our books are volumes
of the same series.

338
00:18:28,400 --> 00:18:29,959
I think the content is connected.

339
00:18:30,640 --> 00:18:32,640
Let's not rush to conclusions.

340
