372
00:22:26,319 --> 00:22:27,800
Hold on.

373
00:22:39,040 --> 00:22:40,920
Is this better?

374
00:23:00,680 --> 00:23:01,719
You look so much

375
00:23:01,719 --> 00:23:03,599
like Su Lie in Love Boys.

376
00:23:04,079 --> 00:23:05,239
You're not him, are you?

377
00:23:05,560 --> 00:23:07,040
No, I'm not.

378
00:23:08,079 --> 00:23:09,319
Then what's your name?

379
00:23:09,560 --> 00:23:12,760
I'm Su... Su Liang.

380
00:23:13,079 --> 00:23:14,119
Su Liang?

381
00:23:15,319 --> 00:23:16,280
Hello, Su Liang.

382
00:23:16,439 --> 00:23:18,520
I'm Zhang Lanlan. Nice to meet you.

383
