386
00:23:55,359 --> 00:23:56,199
Friends?

387
00:23:57,839 --> 00:23:59,400
You must be bored waiting alone.

388
00:23:59,959 --> 00:24:01,160
I'll keep you company
while you're waiting.

389
00:24:14,599 --> 00:24:17,160
