390
00:24:17,479 --> 00:24:18,280
I'm all right.

391
00:24:18,400 --> 00:24:19,760
I'm working as an intern here.

392
00:24:19,880 --> 00:24:21,400
And my house is nearby as well.

393
00:24:21,400 --> 00:24:22,760
I can go back a bit later.

394
00:24:23,280 --> 00:24:24,000
Okay.

395
00:24:29,560 --> 00:24:30,520
Did you bring your phone?

396
00:24:31,160 --> 00:24:32,160
Let's play a game together.

397
00:24:33,880 --> 00:24:34,800
I did.

398
00:24:36,920 --> 00:24:38,800
But I'm not used to it yet.

399
00:24:39,000 --> 00:24:40,079
That's okay. I'll teach you.

400
00:24:40,719 --> 00:24:41,520
Here.

401
00:24:42,640 --> 00:24:43,920
You start this up first.

402
00:24:46,719 --> 00:24:49,439
Right. Then put your hand here.

403
00:24:49,719 --> 00:24:50,479
I'll do the same.

404
00:25:26,719 --> 00:25:28,719
We've searched the night markets,
restaurants and bars.

405
00:25:30,040 --> 00:25:31,640
